      <title>纳斯达克计划推出更多大宗商品、国债 ETF 短期期权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/nasdaq-plans-more-short-term-options-on-commodity-treasury-etfs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纳斯达克公司计划在未来几周内寻求监管部门批准与一系列大宗商品和国债交易所交易基金相关的合约周一到期，这是人们对短期期权兴趣浓厚的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/nasdaq-plans-more-short-term-options-on-commodity-treasury-etfs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 17:53:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
